Fields for cdtestimonials:
- selectableVariant: string (select from "default", "xDemo")
- sortOrder: number
- title: string (section heading)
- subtitle: string (subtitle for the section)
- testimonials: array of objects
    * clientName: string
    * clientCompany: string
    * quote: text
    * logo: image (hotspot true)
- globalComponentSource: reference to cdtestimonials